and finally the Killer.sh platform, which was the most important resource to use when preparing for the CKA exam. You will get two free mock exams when purchasing the CKA exam. It is harder than the actual exam, so if you succeed in passing these mocks within the 2-hour time limit, you can tackle the exam directly and there is no need to revise anymore.

